IMAPAccount personal
Host imap.gmail.com
User adam.trimble@gmail.com
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -s 'imap.gmail.com' -a 'adam.trimble@gmail.com' -w"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

MaildirStore personal-local
Path ~/Mail/adam.trimble-gmail.com/
Inbox ~/Mail/adam.trimble-gmail.com/INBOX

Channel personal-inbox
Master :personal-remote:
Slave :personal-local:INBOX
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-archive
Master :personal-remote:"[Gmail]/Archive"
Slave :personal-local:archive
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-drafts
Master :personal-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :personal-local:drafts
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-sent
Master :personal-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent"
Slave :personal-local:sent
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-trash
Master :personal-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :personal-local:trash
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel personal-junk
Master :personal-remote:"[Gmail]/Spam"
Slave :personal-local:junk
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group personal
Channel personal-inbox
Channel personal-archive
Channel personal-drafts
Channel personal-sent
Channel personal-trash
Channel personal-junk
